com.intel.fightclub.dialog.utils

Class DialogFilesLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.utils.DialogFilesLoader

  • @ThreadSafe
public final class DialogFilesLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for unpacking dialog assets downloaded from the cloud. Also provides methods for retrieving the paths to the various assets.

      • refresh

        public static void refresh(@NonNull
                           android.content.Context context)
        Refreshes the DialogFilesLoader's paths. This is meant to deal with language changes in the app, so that pointers to different CUI assets get updated properly.
        Parameters:
        context - Application context.

      • checkUtteranceDatabases

        public static boolean checkUtteranceDatabases(@NonNull
                                              android.content.Context context)
        Checks if the utterance database assets are found in internal storage. If not found, then this method will check for downloaded zip files and unzip them if available.
        Parameters:
        context - Application context for file operations.
        Returns:
        True if utterance databases are effectively in internal storage, false otherwise.

      • checkDialogFiles

        public static boolean checkDialogFiles(@NonNull
                                       android.content.Context context)
        Checks if the dialog assets are found in internal storage. If they are not found, then the files will be unzipped and placed there.
        Returns:
        True if the dialog assets are present in internal storage.
